response.overview: When a powerful satellite system falls into the hands of Alec Trevelyan, AKA Agent 006, a former ally-turned-enemy, only James Bond can save the world from a dangerous space weapon that -- in one short pulse -- could destroy the earth! As Bond squares off against his former compatriot, he also battles Xenia Onatopp, an assassin who uses pleasure as her ultimate weapon.
response.tagline: No limits. No fears. No substitutes.
response.title: GoldenEye

release_dates.note: Originally a cut 12; uncut and upgraded 2006
